---

<Layout
  title="Treatments & Services | The Face Lab Cotswolds, Lechlade"
  description="Browse our full treatment menu at The Face Lab Cotswolds — brows, lashes, skin treatments, nails, Japanese head spa, massage, lymphatic drainage, aesthetics and more. The Riverside, Lechlade."
>
  <section class="page-hero section">
    <div class="container--text">
      <p class="eyebrow">Cotswolds</p>
      <h1>Treatments — Cotswolds</h1>
      <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem 0;"></div>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">The Riverside, Park End Wharf, Lechlade, GL7 3AQ</p>
      <div class="page-hero__hours">
        <p><strong>Mon</strong> 9am – 5pm</p>
        <p><strong>Tue</strong> 9am – 8pm</p>
        <p><strong>Wed</strong> 9am – 8pm</p>
        <p><strong>Thu</strong> 11am – 6pm</p>
        <p><strong>Fri</strong> 9am – 5pm</p>
        <p><strong>Sat</strong> 10am – 4pm</p>
        <p><strong>Sun</strong> Closed</p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="https://www.fresha.com/a/the-face-lab-cotswolds-lechlade-the-riverside-park-end-wharf-ihomrrjm"
        target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="btn btn--primary"
        style="margin-top: 1.75rem;"
      >Book Online — Cotswolds</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section treatments">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="treatments__note">
        <p>All prices correct as of early 2026. Aesthetic treatments are carried out by Daisy, a fully qualified registered nurse. Prices marked <strong>from</strong> depend on treatment complexity — a complimentary consultation is included with your first appointment.</p>
      </div>
      {treatments.map(group => (
        <div class="treatment-group">
          <h2 class="treatment-group__title">{group.category}</h2>
          <div class="treatment-group__items">
            {group.items.map(item => (
              <div class="treatment-item">
                <div class="treatment-item__info">
                  <p class="treatment-item__name">{item.name}</p>
                  <p class="treatment-item__duration">{item.duration}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="treatment-item__right">
                  {item.badge && <span class="treatment-item__badge">{item.badge}</span>}
                  <p class="treatment-item__price">{item.price}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="book-cta">
    <div class="container book-cta__inner">
      <h2>Ready to book?</h2>
      <p>Book your Cotswolds appointment online via Fresha — instant confirmation.</p>
      <div class="book-cta__btns">
        <a href="https://www.fresha.com/a/the-face-lab-cotswolds-lechlade-the-riverside-park-end-wharf-ihomrrjm" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary">Book Online — Cotswolds</a>
        <a href="/services-witney" class="btn btn--primary">View Witney Menu</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--white); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .page-hero__sub { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; }
  .page-hero__hours { margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; }
  .page-hero__hours p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; }
  .page-hero__hours strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); display: inline-block; width: 2.5rem; }
  .treatments__note { background: var(--accent-light); border: 1px solid rgba(42,13,20,0.12); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; }
  .treatment-group { margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .treatment-group__title { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--soft); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; padding-bottom: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .treatment-item { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0.875rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); gap: 1rem; }
  .treatment-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .treatment-item__name { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); }
  .treatment-item__duration { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--soft); font-weight: 300; margin-top: 0.15rem; }
  .treatment-item__right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 0.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .treatment-item__price { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); white-space: nowrap; }
  .treatment-item__badge { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-light); padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; }
  .book-cta { background: var(--accent); padding: var(--space-xl) 0; text-align: center; }
  .book-cta__inner h2 { color: rgba(250,249,247,0.95); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .book-cta__inner p { color: rgba(250,249,247,0.6); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .book-cta__btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .book-cta__btns .btn--primary { background: rgba(250,249,247,0.12); border-color: rgba(250,249,247,0.3); color: rgba(250,249,247,0.95); }
  .book-cta__btns .btn--primary:hover { background: rgba(250,249,247,0.22); border-color: rgba(250,249,247,0.6); box-shadow: none; }
  @media (max-width: 540px) { .treatment-item { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem; } .treatment-item__right { align-items: flex-start; } }
</style>
